extendedInfo.description: The AFRO News app for Android is a great way to stay up-to-date on National news, D.C. news, Baltimore news, and Sports while on the go. For nearly 120 years the AFRO-American has delivered the most important stories and viewpoints relevant to the Black community surrounding the nation's capitol and across the country, and continues to bring you the major headlines that impact you and your history.The AFRO-American is proud to offer this iPhone application for everyone who wants to stay connected to the daily stories that affect our nation and our world.
